101
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:22,780
♫  If you were by my side,  ♫

102
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:27,499
♫  No matter how many promises we've broken  ♫

103
00:10:27,499 --> 00:10:30,770
♫  There's nothing I'm not willing to do  ♫

104
00:10:30,770 --> 00:10:34,230
♫  Just to have a simple and ordinary life with you  ♫

105
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:37,720
♫  If you were by my side,  ♫

106
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:43,930
♫  All my regrets will be blown away by the wind  ♫

107
00:10:44,695 --> 00:10:45,972
I know you got yourself drunk yesterday.

108
00:10:45,973 --> 00:10:48,534
I bought some ingredients. I'll make you some hangover soup.

109
00:10:48,534 --> 00:10:50,365
No need for that.

110
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:10,240
I thought you...

111
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:16,820
Actually, Fu Zeyi

112
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:19,920
isn't that ruthless.

113
00:11:41,450 --> 00:11:43,380
Fu Zeyi.

114
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:49,600
I'm Lin.

115
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:53,635
I still can't tell who's who.

116
00:11:53,635 --> 00:11:56,064
It's just like the times when I appeared.

117
00:11:56,064 --> 00:11:58,674
You couldn't tell, could you?

118
00:11:58,674 --> 00:12:01,650
But actually, Fu Zeyi and I are quite different.

119
00:12:01,650 --> 00:12:03,290
Look.

120
00:12:03,290 --> 00:12:05,400
I love to cook.

121
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:07,190
But Fu Zeyi hates the smell and the grease.

122
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:09,240
He never steps into the kitchen.

123
00:12:12,570 --> 00:12:16,580
And I like cats, but Fu Zeyi can't tolerate cat fur.

124
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,749
Hurry up! Chase it away!

125
00:12:18,749 --> 00:12:21,464
So both of us are...

126
00:12:37,410 --> 00:12:39,200
Zhixia,

127
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:43,240
I have something important to tell you.

128
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,900
What is it?

129
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,531
I...

130
00:12:47,410 --> 00:12:48,880
Excuse me.

131
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,540
It's fine.

132
00:12:55,707 --> 00:12:57,257
Hello?

133
00:12:58,330 --> 00:12:59,780
What?

134
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:02,249
Okay. I'll be there immediately.

135
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:04,380
What's wrong?

136
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:06,710
Mom suddenly says that she wants to cancel her wedding.

137
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,909
I need to see what's going on. Wait for me.

138
00:13:08,909 --> 00:13:10,780
Can I tag along?

139
00:13:14,290 --> 00:13:15,376
Sure.

140
00:13:15,376 --> 00:13:17,410
I'll wait for you by the door.

141
00:13:17,410 --> 00:13:19,830
[Aizhe Hotel]

142
00:13:27,450 --> 00:13:28,769
What are you doing here again?

143
00:13:28,769 --> 00:13:30,860
Are you still haunting her?

144
00:13:31,850 --> 00:13:33,380
Hello.

145
00:13:36,470 --> 00:13:39,229
This isn't important. I'll explain it to you next time.

146
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:45,080
Sister Jingjing, what's wrong again?

147
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,760
It's all my fault.

148
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,860
I lost the wedding ring.

149
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:49,910
Wait, that's it?

150
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:51,890
How could you be so nonchalant about it?

151
00:13:51,890 --> 00:13:53,570
He actually lost the wedding ring, you know?

152
00:13:53,570 --> 00:13:55,230
Let's cancel the wedding then.

153
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:57,870
Stop being willful. You were fine yesterday.

154
00:13:57,870 --> 00:14:00,100
Did something happen?

155
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:03,189
It's nothing. I just think that it's inauspicious.

156
00:14:03,189 --> 00:14:07,009
Do you know how old you are? Can you be more mature?

157
00:14:07,009 --> 00:14:11,400
So will you proceed with the wedding

158
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:13,660
if we can find the wedding ring for you?

159
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:14,730
Who are you?

160
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:19,980
He's a good friend of mine.

161
00:14:22,254 --> 00:14:24,544
I'll find your wedding ring for you.

162
00:14:30,110 --> 00:14:31,810
This won't do.

163
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:33,580
Wait for me!

164
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,370
I've checked the corridor. There are three surveillance cameras here.

165
00:14:37,370 --> 00:14:38,870
Let's check out the control room.

166
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,360
- Okay.
- Hey.

167
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:45,249
No need for that. There's no need to check the surveillance cameras. I'm sure it wasn't a thief.

168
00:14:45,249 --> 00:14:47,010
How did you know?

169
00:14:47,010 --> 00:14:49,820
Because a cat stole it from me.

170
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,660
- A cat?
- A cat?

171
00:14:51,660 --> 00:14:55,129
That's right. There's a timid cat in the hotel.

172
00:14:55,129 --> 00:14:57,224
I'll look for the cat then.

173
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:01,929
If you want to look for cats, you have to wait until nighttime.

174
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:09,739
Zhixia, do you truly believe that a cat stole her ring?

175
00:15:09,739 --> 00:15:11,750
Why don't we check out the surveillance cameras first?

176
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,930
I'm sure it wasn't a cat.

177
00:15:13,930 --> 00:15:17,129
- But I'm sure it's related to a cat.
- It's related to a cat?

178
00:15:17,129 --> 00:15:19,070
Let's locate the cat for now.

179
00:15:19,070 --> 00:15:22,430
But it's so dark right now.

180
00:15:22,430 --> 00:15:24,680
I can't see anything.

181
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,470
Cats' eyes can reflect light.

182
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:28,420
It's easier to find them during nighttime.

183
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:34,420
By the way, Zhixia, cats love to hide in places like fire extinguisher cabinets or under vehicles.

184
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:36,460
That's why I'm luring it out with cat food.

185
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:39,330
I realized that you're a cat expert.

186
00:15:39,330 --> 00:15:42,189
That's right. I love cats, but I can't keep one

187
00:15:42,189 --> 00:15:44,940
