188
00:15:46,810 --> 00:15:48,520
I found it.

189
00:16:03,490 --> 00:16:06,600
I found you.

190
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,790
We found you.

191
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:10,280
Kitty, where's your home?

192
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:12,660
Take me to your home, okay?

193
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:19,100
Come on.

194
00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:24,760
I found you.

195
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:26,450
There are so many treasures here.

196
00:16:26,450 --> 00:16:29,510
Yeah.

197
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:31,320
Did you find it?

198
00:16:39,430 --> 00:16:41,020
Here you go.

199
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:44,320
It's really here.

200
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:50,430
Jingjing.

201
00:16:58,250 --> 00:17:00,040
We found it.

202
00:17:05,990 --> 00:17:09,009
Jingjing, they found the ring. Please stop being angry, okay?

203
00:17:09,009 --> 00:17:11,770
The ring was indeed stolen by a cat.

204
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:15,140
Sister Jingjing, you're a prophet.

205
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:17,260
Did you know about it from the beginning?

206
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:20,540
- I...
- I thought it was strange.

207
00:17:20,540 --> 00:17:23,870
The cat only kept furry things in its house.

208
00:17:23,870 --> 00:17:27,380
Why did it take your ring all of a sudden?

209
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:31,680
Enough. I admit. I was the one who placed it there.

210
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,500
But why?

211
00:17:37,670 --> 00:17:39,790
- Ye Ming,
- Jingjing.

212
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:42,100
I'm sorry.

213
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:43,825
I'm regretting my decision.

214
00:17:43,825 --> 00:17:45,940
I don't wish to get married.

215
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:52,180
Did I do something wrong?

216
00:17:57,630 --> 00:18:01,260
Zhixia, I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

217
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:03,410
I only cared about my happiness.

218
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:05,940
I neglected your feelings.

219
00:18:05,940 --> 00:18:08,360
If it weren't for last night...

220
00:18:14,850 --> 00:18:18,030
Hello? Zhixia?

221
00:18:18,030 --> 00:18:22,430
No! Don't leave me!

222
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:25,360
Don't leave me!

223
00:18:28,830 --> 00:18:34,250
You misunderstood me completely. I wasn't talking to you back then.

224
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:35,629
You weren't talking to me?

225
00:18:35,629 --> 00:18:39,589
Please go and get married. I wish to obtain happiness, too.

226
00:18:39,589 --> 00:18:42,620
I don't want you to drag me down.

227
00:18:45,070 --> 00:18:48,469
You're still so muddle-headed even though you're getting married tomorrow.

228
00:18:48,469 --> 00:18:51,349
Don't blame me for being a naggy daughter.

229
00:18:51,349 --> 00:18:53,189
You mustn't forget the family rules of the Jian family.

230
00:18:53,189 --> 00:18:56,949
After you're married into his family, you have to do your duties as a wife.

231
00:18:56,949 --> 00:18:58,940
You shouldn't break bowls that shouldn't be broken.

232
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:05,020
Don't ruin clothes that should be washed. Don't look down on others' efforts.

233
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:07,330
That way, no one will make you do any chores in the future.

234
00:19:07,330 --> 00:19:10,420
I swear, as long as Jing Jing marries me,

235
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:15,029
