337
00:27:40,187 --> 00:27:41,960
- Zhixia.
- However, you chose to keep it a secret.

338
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:46,330
Zhixia, I didn't mean to hide the truth from you.

339
00:27:46,330 --> 00:27:48,890
I'm not trying to blame you guys here.

340
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:52,830
No matter if it's Lin or Zeyi,

341
00:27:52,830 --> 00:27:55,919
