359
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:43,800
Mom?

360
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:48,530
Why are you here to drink?

361
00:29:48,530 --> 00:29:50,620
Does Ye Ming know about this?

362
00:29:51,147 --> 00:29:56,190
What do you know? This isn't an alcoholic drink. It's a tonic.

363
00:29:56,190 --> 00:29:59,420
Tonic?

364
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:02,640
Come. Try it.

365
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,700
Mom, I don't want to drink.

366
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:06,700
Try it.

367
00:30:07,330 --> 00:30:10,080
